data.description: Located just off I-26 on Nexton Parkway, proximal to dozens of restaurants and within a few miles from the upcoming ''One Nexton'', ''Downtown Nexton'', and ''The Hub'', you've got to see this stunning pond front home with an upstairs master for yourself. Built in 2020, the entryway is complete with upgraded lvp flooring that extends through the first floor of this open floor plan. There's an office with double doors & powder room on your left as you walk in extending into the living room; opening up towards your dining area and kitchen that boasts granite counter tops that really pop with the espresso finished cabinetry, along with an eat-in Island and stainless steel appliances.All the bedrooms are upstairs along with a secondary family room/loft and laundry room with extra storage.The spacious 2nd floor master bedroom has double walk-in closets and an an en-suite bathroom with floor to ceiling subway tile. The 3 secondary bedrooms are all nicely sized with a shared bath upstairs. Outback is a covered porch and fabulous extended grilling area / uncovered patio with an abundance of room for entertaining. On one of the larger lots in the community, the fully fenced backyard is the perfect place to let the fur babies roam or the kids play. Other characteristics of the home include solar panels to be paid off at closing, surround sound speakers, a front door camera, pre-wired for security system, dual control A/C system, and a 2 car garage for extra storage. Schedule your showings today at this stylishly situated home!
